  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9652514b33ffdd3dc795b7f0ead69e4b.poster.avif?t=1730136693\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9652514b33ffdd3dc795b7f0ead69e4b.webm?t=1730136693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9652514b33ffdd3dc795b7f0ead69e4b.mp4?t=1730136693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Trapped in a buried, forgotten facility, you must reach the core of an ancient machine to rescue your lost lover. System Purge is a challenging, atmospheric, and action-packed 2D platformer.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make it through 7 distinct sectors, from an abandoned weapons laboratory to a vast echo chamber<br></li><li>Survive a wide variety of increasingly deadly threats and obstacles<br></li><li>Discover secrets and complete hidden challenges to decipher the history of the Machine</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9a7eaac9340794f26f64e3af8223ff28.poster.avif?t=1730136693\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9a7eaac9340794f26f64e3af8223ff28.webm?t=1730136693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/9a7eaac9340794f26f64e3af8223ff28.mp4?t=1730136693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515490/extras/66b18d5f640691ff49d76441b688616e.po